summaries.short: The discovery of a mass grave threatens the construction of the airport and places Genny's company at the center of attention.
summaries.full: The discovery of a mass grave threatens the construction of the airport and places Genny's company at the center of attention.

summaries.short: The Capaccio decide to conquer Forcella with severe attacks destined to deprive Sangue Blu and his men of their drug stocks.
summaries.full: The Capaccio decide to conquer Forcella with severe attacks destined to deprive Sangue Blu and his men of their drug stocks. Increasingly alone and running out of raw materials, Enzo runs the risk of losing the loyalty of his men.

summaries.short: The general discontent begins to undermine the leadership of Sangue Blu. The Forcella boys try to find alternative ways to survive.
summaries.full: The general discontent begins to undermine the leadership of Sangue Blu, while the wait for the new cocaine shipment forces the Forcella boys to find alternative ways to survive.

summaries.short: Patriziamust choose: give in to the patriarchy of the Levante clan, or start a war with the family of the man she loves.
summaries.full: Patrizia has discovered that behind all her misfortunes is the hand of her father-in-law, Gerlando. Now she must choose: give in to the patriarchy of the Levante clan and leave the power to Mickey, or start a war with the family of the man she loves.

summaries.short: After the seizure of the cocaine shipment, Nicola decides to follow the trail of the traitor who has sold them to the police.
summaries.full: After the seizure of the cocaine shipment, Nicola, Patrizia's right-hand man, fears losing his boss' trust and decides to follow the trail of the traitor who has sold them to the police.

summaries.short: The clandestine war between Patrizia and the Levantes forces Mickey to choose between his family and the woman he loves.
summaries.full: The clandestine war between Patrizia and the Levantes forces Mickey to choose between his family and the woman he loves. Meanwhile, Genny is not sure he made the right decision.

summaries.short: The peace between the clans is in danger when an operation goes wrong and Patrizia will have to show that she has learned to be in charge.
summaries.full: The outdated patriarchal system of the Levantes tests the relationship between Patrizia and Mickey, Gerlando's favorite son. The peace between the clans is in danger when a cocaine operation goes wrong, and to avoid war, Patrizia will have to show that she has learned what it means to be in charge of the most powerful clan in Naples.
